OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy and
OL,6,Fperhaps thundery showers at first with
OL,7,Fa chance of hail. These will gradually
OL,8,Fease through the evening. It will then
OL,9,Fstay dry overnight with clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Turning cloudy in the west
OL,11,Ftowards dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FDry start with bright spells
OL,14,Fin the east but cloudy with rain in
OL,15,Fwest. Cloud and rain spreading to all
OL,16,Fparts through the day, heaviest rain
OL,17,Fin the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
