OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry and breezy on Friday and Saturday
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells and some showers
OL,8,Fpossible. Dry on Sunday with long
OL,9,Fperiods of sunshine developing.
